[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Service interval aircraft]]
With this feature, you can set the number of days an aircraft will wait since its last service before it will go to a depot to be serviced again. This can also be set to '''disabled''', then you can add go to depot orders allowing you to have better control over when an aircraft is serviced.
